# ── Telegram Bot ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Open Telegram → search @BotFather → send /newbot → follow prompts → get token
# 2. Both you and Ivan must open the bot and press Start
# 3. To find chat IDs: paste this URL in a browser (replace TOKEN):
#    https://api.telegram.org/bot<TOKEN>/getUpdates
#    After each of you sends any message to the bot, your chat_id appears in the JSON.
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=your_telegram_bot_token_here
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID_YULIIA=your_numeric_chat_id
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID_IVAN=ivans_numeric_chat_id
